msgid "Poudriere"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/testing/chapter.adoc:118
msgid ""
"For a ports contributor, Poudriere is one of the most important and helpful "
"testing and build tools. Its main features include:"
